OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FAs Maria read through more of the old
OL,7,Fdocuments, she came across something
OL,8,Fthat would change her life forever - a
OL,9,Fnewspaper clipping revealing her
OL,10,Fmother had been murdered.
OL,12,FOn 20th May 1973, Catia Rimondi was
OL,13,Fcelebrating her 21st birthday with
OL,14,Ffriends at the popular Alexandria
OL,15,Fnightclub in Newport.
OL,17,FEarly the next morning, she was found
OL,18,Fdead just a mile from her home.
