OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FPolice launched a murder investigation
OL,7,Fand soon focused on a man named Robert
OL,8,FDavies, who had been seen leaving the
OL,9,Fnightclub with Catia after offering
OL,10,Fher a lift.
OL,12,FCatia never made it home.
OL,14,FDavies took her to the woods, where he
OL,15,Fstabbed her multiple times and left
OL,16,Fher body in a stream.
