OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FRetired Gwent Police Detective Chief
OL,7,FInspector Gerry Johnson, who was part
OL,8,Fof the investigation, said Davies
OL,9,Fconfessed to the murder while being
OL,10,Ftaken to the police station for
OL,11,Fquestioning.
OL,13,F"He didn't appear agitated in any way
OL,14,Fwhatsoever," Gerry said.
OL,16,F"He seemed quite calm, very matter of
OL,17,Ffact. He's the last type of person I'd
OL,18,Fhave thought would have used that type
OL,19,Fof violence."
