OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FMore than 50 years later, Maria is
OL,7,Fstill searching for answers about why
OL,8,Fher mother was killed.
OL,10,F"Only he knows the truth," she said.
OL,11,F"There are so many different things
OL,12,FI've read in the papers, I just want
OL,13,Fto get to the truth.
OL,15,F"I'd ask him how well he knew her. Did
OL,16,Fthey have a relationship? What was she
OL,17,Flike as a person? And why he did what
OL,18,Fhe did.
