OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,F"I'd quite happily sit there and ask
OL,7,Fthose questions face to face, just to
OL,8,Fsee if he could look me in the eye."
OL,10,FDavies was sentenced to life in prison
OL,11,Ffor Catia's murder but was released
OL,12,Fafter serving 15 years. After
OL,13,Freturning to Newport, ten years later,
OL,14,Fshockingly, he went on to kill again.
OL,16,FIn September 1999, he murdered Graham
OL,17,F"Budgie" Mills, who was a witness in a
OL,18,Fsexual assault case against him.
OL,19,FDavies denied carrying out the offence.
