OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FDavies then went on the run, living in
OL,7,Fa hide in Draethen Quarry near
OL,8,FCaerphilly. A huge police search was
OL,9,Flaunched and he was caught and jailed
OL,10,Ffor a second time.
OL,12,FBudgie's brother, Royston Mills, said
OL,13,Fhe is still haunted by the killing and
OL,14,Fquestions why Davies was ever released.
OL,16,F"You're never going to get over it,"
OL,17,Fhe said. "He's just ruined us all and
OL,18,Fwe're paying for it every day of our
OL,19,Flives.
