OL,6,F"Any man who's killed somebody, gone
OL,7,Fto jail and then come out and done it
OL,8,Fagain, there's got to be something not
OL,9,Fright. He should never be out, in
OL,10,Fanybody's eyes."
OL,12,FBy law, prisoners serving life
OL,13,Fsentences can apply for parole every
OL,14,Ftwo years after completing their
OL,15,Fminimum term. Robert Davies is due to
OL,16,Fhave his next review in 2026.
