OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Parole Board
OL,7,Fsaid: "Every serious further offence
OL,8,Fis a tragedy in which victims and
OL,9,Ftheir families' lives are affected
OL,10,Fforever.
OL,12,F"Whilst these represent a tiny
OL,13,Fproportion of cases considered, one
OL,14,Fcase is one too many and we take these
OL,15,Fextremely seriously.
OL,17,F"Where this happens, the Parole Board
OL,18,Fis committed to doing everything it
OL,19,Fcan to learn the lessons that will
OL,20,Fhelp to prevent further tragedies."
