OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Robert Davies will only be
OL,8,Freleased if the Parole Board - which
OL,9,Fis independent of government - decides
OL,10,Fit is safe after a thorough risk
OL,11,Fassessment.
OL,13,F"Even if released, he will be
OL,14,Fmonitored by the Probation Service and
OL,15,Fcan be brought back to jail to keep
OL,16,Fthe public safe."
