OL,3,C'I just want the truth': Daughter of
OL,4,Cmurdered Newport woman seeks answers
OL,6,FMaria describes her life as "a jigsaw
OL,7,Fwith missing pieces." She knows she
OL,8,Fwill never meet her mother, but she
OL,9,Fhopes she may be able to find out more
OL,10,Fabout her father.
OL,12,F"He was called Timothy and they knew
OL,13,Feach other for four months, that's all
OL,14,FI know," she said. "My mother's
OL,15,Ffriends may still be alive. Do they
OL,16,Fknow anything?"
OL,18,FMaria's story and her search for
OL,19,Finformation about her mother and her
OL,20,Fdeath is told in My Mum, Murder and
OL,21,FMe, available now on ITVX.
